-- 本月入库
SELECT material_code             物料编码,
       sum(in_stock_qty)              数量
FROM mm_prod_finished_in_bill
WHERE created_dt >= DATE_FORMAT(DATE_ADD(NOW(), INTERVAL -1 MONTH), '%Y-%m-01')
  AND created_dt < DATE_FORMAT(NOW(), '%Y-%m-01')
  AND in_stock_warehouse_number = 0301
GROUP BY material_code;
